        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 46. Living snails from Bau A Japonia barbata (L. Pfeiffer, 1855) ME 8768 Gunung Kapor B Opisthophorus euryomphalus (L. Pfeiffer, 1856) ME 8779 Gunung Kapor C Opisthophorus biciliatus Mousson, 1849 ME 8754 Gunung Kapor D Opisthophorus birostris (L. Pfeiffer, 1854) ME 8755 Gunung Kapor. All not to scale." , "Figure 7. A Opisthophorus biciliatus (Mousson, 1849) ME 8754 Gunung Kapor B Opisthophorus birostris (L. Pfeiffer, 1854) ME 8758 Gunung Kapor C Opisthophorus cavernae (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 8904 Gunung Doya D Opisthophorus euryomphalus (L. Pfeiffer, 1856) ME 8779 Gunung Kapor E Platyrhaphe linita (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 0881 Gunung Batu F Pterocyclos tenuilabiatus (Metcalfe, 1851) ME 5910 Gunung Batu." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/536834" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/536795" .

